  "number": 5100,
  "title": "Melchizedek",
  "comment": "``King of Righteousness'': king and priest of Salem, who blessed Abraham. David assumed Melchizedek's role as king and priest of Jersualem for himself and his descendants. Jesus Christ succeeded to this role and became a high priest in the order of Melchizedek.",
  "refgroup": null,
  "children": [],
